input_text:
Generate 8 training examples for sentiment analysis with priority detection.

Target Schema:
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "sentiment": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["positive", "negative", "neutral", "mixed"]
    },
    "priority": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["urgent", "high", "normal", "low"]
    },
    "summary": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Brief summary of the main point"
    },
    "action_required": {
      "type": "boolean"
    }
  },
  "required": ["sentiment", "priority"]
}

Ensure all enum values are covered across the examples.
